                            <td width="147"><p>&nbsp; </p></td>
                            <td width="428" valign="top"><p align="left">RedMonk Analyst Stephen  O'Grady, on a Massachusetts proposal to require all State documents to be saved  in OpenDocument or pdf formats<a href="http://news.zdnet.com/2100-3513_22-5845451.html">...Full Story</a></p></td>
