                      <strong>The Edge Daily,  September 21, 2005 -- </strong>The Islamic Financial Services Board (IFSB) is  organising the Islamic Financial Services Forum: The<strong> </strong>European Challenge,  which will be hosted by the Banque Centrale Du Luxembourg (Central Bank of  Luxembourg). The forum will be held on Nov 8&ndash;9, 2005 in Luxembourg. IFSB is an  international-standard setting body of regulatory and supervisory agencies for  the Islamic financial services industry. ...<a href="http://www.theedgedaily.com/cms/content.jsp?id=com.tms.cms.article.Article_77b37a53-cb73c03a-90fa0500-698f1752">Full Story</a></p>
